songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Feel like a bird
As it perched in a tree
Feel like a knife
As it burrows into me

[Chorus]
Love is not a game
Take my word for it, oh
Love does not explain
Take my word for it, oh

[Verse 2]
Feel like a bird
With a broken wing
Feel like a knife
As it cuts into me

[Chorus]
Love is not a game
Take my word for it, oh
Love does not explain
Take my word for it, oh

[Outro]
Feel like a bird
As it perched in a tree
songs.title: Like A Bird
